room_title: Escape room "The Library" by The Panel Room Escape Games in St. Joseph (MO)
room_address: 107 South 4th Street, 2nd Floor, St Joseph, MO 64501
room_description: A big shot attorney working on a high-profile case needs your help. He is out of the country and left behind key evidence for his client's upcoming trial. To keep the information out of the wrong hands, the attorney has hidden the evidence behind a maze of puzzles, riddles, and clues. Your task is to decipher the solution and transmit the evidence before time runs out.
